eedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nqg1665702709724.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nqg1665702709724.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nqg1665702709724.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nqg1665702709724\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Panel\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Panel is a Development Object that defines a toolbar containing buttons to execute structure editor functions and operations on the active form.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__section_w501ab1b5b1_w502ab1b5_w503ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__section_w504ab1b5b3_w505ab1b5_w506ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d240537e56\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">pnl</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijz1665702550775.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijz1665702550775.html\" title=\"An Untyped Library is a Main Development Object that defines a collection of objects that may be of different types, and which can be reused or accessed by other objects during development or at runtime.\">Untyped Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PanelName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>.pnl</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nqg1665702709724__table_d10697e1_d10698e1_d10699e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lib:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>:pnl:<var class=\"keyword varname\">PanelName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__section_w507ab1b5b5_w508ab1b5_w509ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d240537e262\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__p_d96269e1_d96270e1_d96271e1\">Panel specializes Development Object in the following\n            ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39002e1_d39003e1_d39004e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__p_d96272e1_d96273e1_d96274e1\">It has a runtime library as parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39005e1_d39006e1_d39007e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__p_d96275e1_d96276e1_d96277e1\">It has no child development objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__section_w510ab1b5b7_w511ab1b5_w512ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d240537e286\"> Properties </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39008e1_d39009e1_d39010e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39011e1_d39012e1_d39013e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ymp1665702709794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ymp1665702709794.html\" title=\"Function to include in the panel. A function can be a user-defined operation or a structure editor function, or it can represent a new line or a separator.\">Function</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39014e1_d39015e1_d39016e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vkx1665702687952.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkx1665702687952.html\" title=\"This property determines whether buttons for character attributes (bold, italics, and underline) are displayed when the panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are True or False.\">Character Attributes</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39017e1_d39018e1_d39019e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xmm1665702688023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmm1665702688023.html\" title=\"Determines whether buttons for View, Overstrike, and Previous mode should appear in the panel when it is used as a session panel.\">View</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39020e1_d39021e1_d39022e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zga1665702688096.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zga1665702688096.html\" title=\"Number of available Uniface character sets (Font 0 through Font 7) for which a button is displayed when this panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are 0 through 7.\">Font Range</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39023e1_d39024e1_d39025e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfq1665702709863.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfq1665702709863.html\" title=\"Height of the panel button, in character cells.\">Height</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39026e1_d39027e1_d39028e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sag1665702709934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sag1665702709934.html\" title=\"Width of the button, in characters.\">Width</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39029e1_d39030e1_d39031e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nct1665702710006.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nct1665702710006.html\" title=\"Name of the operation activated by this button. If the operation does not exist in the form with which that this panel is associated, this button is disabled.\">Operation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"nqg1665702709724__li_d39032e1_d39033e1_d39034e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uzw1665702710075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uzw1665702710075.html\" title=\"Name of the glyph to be used as the icon of an operation button in a form panel. If there is a message with the same name as the glyph, it is used as the tooltip for the button.\">Glyph Name &amp; Message Text</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614862\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Panel Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Panel A Panel is a Development Object that defines a toolbar containing buttons to execute structure editor functions and operations on the active form. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: pnl Main Development Object? No Part of: Untyped Library Contains: Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation output: PanelName @ Library .pnl URI format: lib: LibraryName :pnl: PanelName Specialization Panel specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a runtime library as parent object. It has no child development objects. Properties Description Function Character Attributes View Font Range Height Width Operation Glyph Name & Message Text Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}